The Vulkan spec states: descriptorPool must have enough free descriptor capacity remaining to allocate the descriptor sets of the specified layouts (https://www.khronos.org/registry/vulkan/specs/1.0/html/vkspec.html#VUID-VkDescriptorSetAllocateInfo-descriptorPool-00307)
Unloading layer library libVkLayer_MESA_device_select.so
Unloading layer library libVkLayer_khronos_validation.so
